  <name>Fan Control</name>
  <summary>Control your laptop fan speed</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      A simple GTK frontend for nbfc-linux. Switch between automatic, maximum
      and manual fan modes, set a custom speed with a slider, and watch the
      current speed on an animated fan gauge.
    </p>
    <p>Requires nbfc-linux installed and its service running on the host.</p>
  </description>

  <launchable type="desktop-id">io.github.andre0n.FanControl.desktop</launchable>

